<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4693605>
    dc:description "FIGURES 165–167. Allograpta exoticus (Wiedemann, 1830): (165) female in Rosa sp. (photo by Miguel Mellado). Allograpta hortensis (Philippi, 1865): (166) male on Leucheria sp. (photo by Daniel Llavaneras). Allograpta pulchra Shannon, 1927: (167) male on Orizoë sp. (photo by Daniel Llavaneras)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4693605/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4693611>
    dc:description "FIGURE 170. Distribution map of Allograpta species in Chile: Allograpta exoticus (Wiedemann, 1830) (blue circles); Allograpta hortensis (Philippi, 1865) (red circles); Allograpta pulchra Shannon, 1927 (black circles); Allograpta piurana Shannon, 1927 (green circles) and Allograpta robinsoniana Enderlein, 1938 (yellow circles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4693611/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

